": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Aadil, mere aur mere farzand ke qaatilo’n ke darmiyaan faisla farma. Ay Aadil aur qaadir, mere aur mere farzand ke qaatilo’n ke darmiyaan faisla farma. Ay haakim, mere aur mere farzand ke qaatilo’n ke darmiyaan faisla farma.", "Urdu": "اے حاکم، میرے اور میرے فرزند کے قاتلوں کے درمیان فیصلہ فرما۔", "RArabic": "YAA A’DLO OHKUM BAYNEE WA BAYNA QAATELE WALADEE. YAA A’DLO, YAA JABBAARO, OHKUM BAYNEE WA BAYNA QAATELE WALADEE. YAA HAKAMA, OHKUM BAYNEE WA BAYNA QAATELE WALADEE.", "ArabicText1": "یَا حَكَمُ، اُحْكُمْ بَیْنِیْ وَبَیْنَ قَاتِلِ وَلَدِیْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign1